name: Laffey (Azur Lane)
description:
Use to 1 ~ 0.8

You can create a total of 9 outfits.

She can change into different outfits and hairstyles by filling out the prompts!

The keywords are '(costume), fake_animal_ears'.

If her outfit is not generating well, write additional prompts.

1.Normal

laffey, fake_animal_ears, camisole, pink_jacket

2.Retrofit

retrofit, fake animal ears, bikini, skirt, jacket,

3.Wedding

wedding_dress, fake animal ears, blue_ribbon,

4.Snow Rabbit and Candy Apple

kimono, fake_animal_ears,

5.White Rabbit Welcomes the Spring

hanfu, fake_animal_ears,

6.Bunny Clerk?

school_uniform, fake animal ears, navel, hat,

7.Picnic Adventure?

picnic_dress, fake animal ears, jacket,

8.Bunny Idol @Unmotivated

idol, fake_animal_ears, navel,

9.Sleep to Clean Another Day

sleepwear, fake_animal_ears, pink_pajamas,
